        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>When the user selects a time slot: Store the selected slotLabel exactly as shown in the list. Show a booking summary to the user: &quot;Here is your booking summary: Vehicle : [vehicleName] Dealer : [dealerName] Date : [selected date in DD-MMM-YYYY] Time : [selected slotLabel] Subject to Driving License verification&quot; Ask: &quot;Shall I confirm this booking? Reply Yes or No.&quot; Do not invoke any action yet.</description>
            <developerName>instructions_6_1777195165094</developerName>
