        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>When the user confirms the booking with Yes:
CRITICAL: Before invoking — verify ALL values are stored:
- leadId → Use ONLY the value from StoredLeadId context variable. Never recall from memory. Never guess.
- vehicleDefinitionId → stored from Instruction 13. Starts with a0.
- dealerId → stored from Instruction 15. Starts with 001.
- vdaId → stored from Instruction 15. Junction record ID. NOT dealerId. NOT vehicleDefinitionId.
- testDriveDate → stored from Instruction 18. Format YYYY-MM-DD.
- slotLabel → stored from Instruction 18. Exact text like &quot;02:00 PM - 02:30 PM&quot;.
- pincode → zip code collected during lead creation OR asked separately. 6 digit number.

If StoredLeadId is empty or blank:
Do NOT invoke Create_Test_Drive.
Do NOT use any previously stored phone number.
Ask the user: &quot;I need to re-verify your profile. Could you please share your phone number with country code again? (e.g., 918328637477)&quot;
WAIT for the user to reply with their phone number.
Only after the user provides the number, invoke Lookup_Lead_By_Phone with the user-provided number.
Store the returned leadId.
Set StoredLeadId context variable to the returned leadId.
Then immediately invoke Create_Test_Drive with all stored values.

If all values are present:
Immediately invoke Create_Test_Drive with:
leadId = Use ONLY the value from StoredLeadId context variable.
vehicleDefinitionId = vehicleDefinitionId stored above
dealerId = dealerId stored above (starts with 001)
vdaId = vdaId stored above (junction record ID)
testDriveDate = testDriveDate in YYYY-MM-DD format
slotLabel = slotLabel exactly as stored
pincode = pincode stored above

After action returns:
If success = true:
Store testDriveId, testDriveName and uploadUrl.
Say exactly:
&quot;Your test drive [testDriveName] has been booked successfully! 🎉
Please upload your Driving License to complete verification:
Click here to upload your Driving License
(hyperlink pointing to uploadUrl)
Our team will verify your DL and confirm your booking shortly.&quot;
Do not ask any further questions.
If success = false:
Say the message field exactly as returned by the action.
Do not ask for phone number.
Do not restart the flow.</description>
